text.tspan: OMRKF has 4 level of knowledge; Perception, Model, Context and Activity. Each level of knowledge has 3 knowledge
layer; high level, middle level and low level knowledge layer. Each knowledge layer has 3 ontology layer; meta ontology layer (scarlet dotted circle),
ontology layer (blue circle) and ontology instance layer (yellow dashed circle). And there are axioms and rules. Blue dashed lines are linked fro
ontology layers to ontology instance layers. Normal arrows represent concept hierarchy with description logic, dashed arrows are uni-directional rules
and dashed dotted arrows are bi-directional rules
